snippet.title: AVATAR 3: FIRE AND ASH - Trailer (2025) James Cameron | 20th century studios
snippet.description:
#avatar #jamescameron #disney 

— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— AVATAR 3: FIRE AND ASH

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

—  In this concept trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash, the story picks up after the events of The Way of Water, as Colonel Quaritch survives and seeks refuge among the Mangkwan Clan — a fierce fire-based Na'vi tribe led by the unrelenting Varang. Through Jake Sully’s solemn voice-over, the trailer explores themes of vengeance, fractured beliefs, and the unbreakable bonds of family. As war brews across the scorched lands of Pandora, Jake warns of a new kind of enemy — one that fights without faith and burns without mercy. The trailer culminates in a fiery buildup, anchored by Sully’s powerful declaration: 'Sullys stick together,' signaling that while fire may rise, unity will endure.

snippet.title: Race Highlights | 2025 Belgian Grand Prix

snippet.title: Saifond Hypocrite (Clip Officiel By Mintigui Prod
snippet.description:
Hypocrite 

Moi, je n’ai nul besoin de l’aide des hypocrites 
Moi seul, je travaille et je fais des hits
Leurs cœurs ne sont pas purs, mais obscurcis 
C’est pourquoi je m’éloigne d’eux pour avoir la paix. 
C’est souvent tes proches qui salissent ton nom. 
C’est souvent tes connaissances qui te salissent 
Je prie et je demande à Dieu de me protéger en récitant les trois dernières sourates du coran. 
Pour m’échapper d’eux, de l’intérieur comme de l’extérieur

Ils veulent tous qu’on soit proche. 
Mais cette proximité ne me sert à rien.  
Qu’ils dégagent.
Qu’Allah donne longue vie à mes ennemis. 
Pour qu’ils se mordent le doigt afin de savoir dans ce monde, chacun a son moment. 

Les hypocrites disent qu’ils vont m’aider,
Je leur ai dit non 
Je sais qu’ils me freineront
Je leur ai dit non
Je ne veux pas de leur aide. 
Je leur ai dit non
Je leur ai dit non
Non, non, non 

Les hypocrites disent qu’ils vont m’aider,
Je leur ai dit non 
Je sais qu’ils me freineront
Je leur ai dit non
Je ne veux pas de leur aide. 
Je leur ai dit non
Je leur ai dit non
Non, non, non 

My God never let me down 
Look at me How 
my ennemies so leave me 
my god bless me

N’accepte pas que d’autres gens t’aident,
Ils te freineront.
Si tu leur dépasses, ils te saliront. 
Derrière toi ils sont mauvais, 
À ta présence, ils t’applaudissent. 
Ne crois pas à tout le monde,
D’autres ne sont pas reconnaissants. 
Moi, c’est à Dieu que je sollicite de l’aide.
Car lui, il me fermera jamais la porte.
Moi, si on se rapproche, c’est sûr la sincérité. 
Moi, je ne suis pas dans l’hypocrisie.

snippet.title: Madonna - La Isla Bonita (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
🍕Madonna - La Isla Bonita (Lyrics)

🍕Lyrics:

[Intro]
¿Cómo puede ser verdad?

[Verse 1]
Last night I dreamt of San Pedro
Just like I'd never gone, I knew the song
Young girl with eyes like the desert
It all seems like yesterday, not far away

[Chorus]
Tropical the island breeze, all of nature wild and free
(Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah)
This is where I long to be, La Isla Bonita
And when the samba played, the sun would set so high
(Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah)
Ring through my ears and sting my eyes, your Spanish lullaby

[Verse 2]
I fell in love with San Pedro
Warm wind carried on the sea, he called to me
Te dijo, "Te amo"
I prayed that the days would last, they went so fast

[Chorus]
Tropical the island breeze, all of nature wild and free
(Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah)
This is where I long to be, La Isla Bonita
And when the samba played, the sun would set so high
(Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah)
Ring through my ears and sting my eyes, your Spanish lullaby

[Bridge]
I want to be where the sun warms the sky
When it's time for siesta, you can watch them go by
Beautiful faces, no cares in this world
Where a girl loves a boy, and a boy loves a girl

[Pre-Chorus]
Last night I dreamt of San Pedro
It all seems like yesterday, not far away

[Chorus]
Tropical the island breeze, all of nature wild and free
(Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah)
This is where I long to be, La Isla Bonita
And when the samba played, the sun would set so high
(Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah)
Ring through my ears and sting my eyes, your Spanish lullaby
(Pa-pa-pa-pa-pa)
Tropical the island breeze, all of nature wild and free
(Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah)
This is where I long to be, La Isla Bonita
And when the samba played, the sun would set so high
(Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah)
Ring through my ears and sting my eyes, your Spanish lullaby

[Outro]
La-la-la-la-la-la-la
Te dijo, "Te amo"
La-la-la-la-la-la-la
Él dijo que te ama
Pa-pa-pa-pa-pa-pa-pa-pa (Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah)
La Isla Bonita
Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah
Spanish lullaby

Le jeu a un public conséquent à l'international, mais au niveau francophone, excepté quelques créateurs de contenu, ça n'a jamais été un jeu extrêmement populaire. (On ne remercie jamais assez Aiekillu pour les travaux concernant Kenshi);

snippet.description:

Check out my Spotify playlist: https://spoti.fi/2Jba0lx

https://soundcloud.com/creativchaos

https://www.tiktok.com/@creative.chaos_
https://www.facebook.com/creatvchaos
https://x.com/crevtivechaos
https://www.instagram.com/creativ.chaos

Lyrics:

[Verse 1]
Finished with my woman
'Cause she couldn't help me with my mind
People think I'm insane
Because I am frowning all the time

[Verse 2]
All day long I think of things
But nothing seems to satisfy
Think I'll lose my mind
If I don't find something to pacify

[Bridge]
Can you help me
Occupy my brain?
Oh yeah

[Verse 3]
I need someone to show me
The things in life that I can't find
I can't see the things that make true happiness
I must be blind

[Guitar Solo]

[Verse 4]
Make a joke and I will sigh
And you will laugh and I will cry
Happiness, I cannot feel
And love to me is so unreal

[Verse 5]
And so, as you hear these words
Telling you now of my state
I tell you to enjoy life
I wish I could, but it's too late
